### 1. Get Scores for a Class Subject
GET http://localhost:3000/routes/api/score/scorebyclass?classSubjectId=1
Content-Type: application/json

### 2. Save Scores (Bulk Insert/Update)
POST http://localhost:3000/routes/api/score/scores
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "classSubjectId": 1,
  "assessmentTypeId": 1,
  "scores": [
    {
      "studentId": 1,
      "score": 85.5
    },
    {
      "studentId": 2,
      "score": 90
    },
    {
      "studentId": 3,
      "score": 75
    }
  ]
}

